{"tid":1500162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MTR 不合作運動升級 - 直接爆閘唔比錢或用長者卡","createTime":"2019-08-24T03:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T10:55:01.000Z","uid":250979,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d54a50e19d598e19ec5a1d00add37ae1d663a192","tid":1500162,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"之前所做既塞鐵, 除非配合擺工, 否則只會令返工遲到, 同時被中間派指責, 成效不大<br />\n但以家應該直接用長者卡或爆閘, 只要人數足夠, 佢唔敢過黎CHECK<br />\n而且就算交罰款, 你亦都可以唔交, 而且無息, 佢最終只可以向小額錢債審裁處到告你<br />\n到時交十蚊, 然後就話交左, 佢又要再告, 拖長黎搞佢就唔再煩你<br />\n希望呢方面有律司巴打補充<br />\n<br />\nMTR 坐大係因為係有無限的經濟收益, 令佢收入減少, 係最直接既打擊"},{"pid":"a11359f4853af6884bdc66dee09bf7caa9b7e2e9","tid":1500162,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3c0c46d58873b6f55930ad76c87a1d5390b6178","tid":1500162,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a382077e1624bb620e0a5a5105de4ce744e20ce7","tid":1500162,"uid":187201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa85d8bb6c00d950bf59b89bab6c384b2d7ceff","tid":1500162,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45a5760b9069960252d57ca1930707fa7124397","tid":1500162,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a38691c37163df3f21792893288b54ea2563c774","tid":1500162,"uid":81921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"巴士封路，狗鐵停駛，不合作助攻，觀塘兵家死地走唔到，去機場，捉緊春袋"},{"pid":"12228b5cde56f73b3bdc3f92125abe329431f12f","tid":1500162,"uid":25